Date: Wed, Jun 19, 2013 at 9:23 PM<br>Subject: Call for partners: Evaluation support for programmes that economically empower women in sub-Saharan Africa<br>To: <br>Cc: Katie Chapman &lt;<a href="mailto:K-Chapman@..." target="_blank">K-Chapman@...</a>&gt;<br>


